_revenue":3.147,"earnings_growth":0.269,"shares_outstanding":62611245.0,"float_shares":7837737.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.81172997,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":-0.729,"fifty_two_week_high":126.05,"fifty_two_week_low":32.5,"fifty_day_average":43.5338,"two_hundred_day_avg":73.74435,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":141.65,"all_time_low":32.5,"long_business_summary":"Alphalogic Techsys Limited, together with its subsidiary, provides information technology consulting solutions and support services in India. It operates through Information Technology, Biofuels, and Investment segments. The company designs and develops web applications in e-commerce, e-learning, analytics, finance, entertainment, healthcare, and real estate domains, including web portal, custom web application development, enterprise portal, and responsive website development services; and mobile applications for iOS, android, and cross platforms, as well as offers app store submission services and web services and APIs. It also involved the consulting and business intelligence, and analytics services, such as extract, transform, and load process; and data warehousing, data visualization, data mining, big data, and enterprise analytics. In addition, the company provides digital product strategy and consulting services; UI/UX design and consulting services, which include responsive web and mobile designs, tailored dashboard design, wireframes, mock-ups, and rapid prototyping, and GUI testing; and DevOps consulting services and solutions comprising continuous integration/continuous deployment, deployment automation and services, and testing automation and security services. Further, the company engages in the design, manufacturing, supply, and installation of industrial racks and storage solutions. Additionally, it offers ethanol and allied products. It serves healthcare, SaaS Software, e-commerce, and fintech industries. The company was formerly known as Alphalogic Inc and changed its name to Alphalogic Techsys Limited in December 2018. Alphalogic Techsys Limited was founded in 2008 and is based in Pune, India."}}